{"tid":966692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果阿爺廚房係用美女廚房既模式去拍 會唔會吸引過依家鼎爺煮 譚玉瑛附和既玩法","createTime":"2019-01-03T03:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T05:10:56.000Z","uid":92376,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1833a4dd9e460046c3e210a52c45fd53e51845e8","tid":966692,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:50:07.000Z","msg":"《阿爺廚房》重新開放，吸引一眾年過六旬的男藝員到場大顯廚藝。他們走進廚房前，只簡單聽過菜名及幾十秒的流程簡介便要動手，能否以廚藝俘虜一眾女嘉賓的胃？阿爺烹調指定菜式時，大賣神秘感，要女嘉賓猜猜他們是誰，還歡迎觀眾參與競猜！每集指定一種新鮮食材，讓阿爺按指定主題發揮創意烹煮，務求從評判手上取得高分數，爭奪新一屆阿爺廚神稱號。還有一眾阿叔學徒，研發賣相不夠好、配搭怪異但實際美味的「新奇料理」！<br />\n<br />\n第一集嘉賓：<br />\n鷲哥 劉江 熊樹根<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad6f2645ebedef54886b5a16c24cbbea9958322","tid":966692,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b875ab0926650dd088385a2830a57ccf13eaf05c","tid":966692,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ad6f2645ebedef54886b5a16c24cbbea9958322","tid":966692,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:51:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:52:19.000Z","msg":"見到女評判？"},{"pid":"6eb9c45efe736173fb849a2d4c164dae1ebbc7f6","tid":966692,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"以為你話搵鮑姐、 司棋姐嚟煮"},{"pid":"f850f9358136af599088bb5fc779a20c594f1991","tid":966692,"uid":92376,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6eb9c45efe736173fb849a2d4c164dae1ebbc7f6","tid":966692,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:52:37.000Z","msg":"以為你話搵鮑姐、 司棋姐嚟煮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:55:11.000Z","msg":"佢地係男人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class